I think this crash was caused by null value of Menu object:

```
    public boolean onPrepareOptionsMenu(Menu menu) {
        menu.findItem(R.id.menu_share).setVisible(mItem != null);
        return mItem != null;
    }
```

Although this situation is not frequent, but I think this is a danguous behavior that you invoke a method without the judgement of null :).
